# API & Integrations

## 1. Purpose
- Define system integrations and API endpoints
- Ensure BV-based logic is applied consistently
- Support future digital and physical products

## 2. Authentication
- All API calls require secure authentication
- Users are authenticated by BV activation status

## 3. Product & BV APIs
- Endpoints for digital/physical product listing
- BV assignment and accumulation
- Repurchase BV contribution
- Activation check (BV 2100)

## 4. Income & Level APIs
- APIs for level income calculation (up to 30 levels)
- APIs for repurchase distribution
- BV-first calculation only, price-independent

## 5. CTO Royalty APIs
- Track pin qualification
- Calculate CTO Royalty based on BV & pins
- Equal distribution per system rules

## 6. Notes
- Future add-on products can integrate via same API structure
- No API exposes guaranteed income
- System logic remains consistent for all user roles
